<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="supp-images" xml:lang="en">
    <head>Images, figures and facsimile</head>
    <p>It is possible to link to digital versions of photographs, drawings, squeezes and other images or
        representations of the text (or other views of the support) using the <gi>facsimile</gi> element.
    </p>
    
    <p>
        <specList>
            <specDesc key="facsimile"/>
            <specDesc key="surface"/>
            <specDesc key="graphic"/>
        </specList>
    </p>
    
    <p>
        discussion to be added
    </p>
    
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples">
        <facsimile>
            <graphic url="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/images/photo/full/77_AA_33.jpg"/>
        </facsimile>
    </egXML>
    
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples">
        <facsimile>
            <graphic url="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/images/photo/full/78_G_20.jpg"><desc>Squeeze (1978)</desc></graphic>
            <graphic url="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/images/photo/full/94_D_16.jpg"><desc>Photograph of monument (1994)</desc></graphic>
            <graphic url="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/images/photo/full/smith-ala32.jpg"><desc>Drawing of reconstructed monument (1999)</desc></graphic>
        </facsimile>
    </egXML>
    
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples">
        <facsimile>
            <surface n="i"><desc>Face of inscribed base</desc>
                <graphic url="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/images/photo/full/72_L_27A.jpg"><desc>Photograph (1972)</desc></graphic>
                <graphic url="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/images/photo/full/NY_pr_046.jpg"><desc>Squeeze</desc></graphic>
            </surface>
            <surface><desc>Top of base</desc>
                <graphic url="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/images/photo/full/NY_94_55_03.jpg"><desc>Photograph (1994)</desc></graphic>
            </surface>
            <surface><desc>Inscription on head of statue</desc>
                <graphic url="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/images/photo/full/smith-ala254.jpg"><desc>Drawing (2001)</desc></graphic>
            </surface>
        </facsimile>
    </egXML>
    
